      "description": "## CPU Usage\n\n#### Description\nTracks the container cpu usage for the valheim docker container\n\n#### Source\nThis panel sources a variety of information exposed by cadvisor. Refer to [monitoring docker with cadvisor](https://prometheus.io/docs/guides/cadvisor/) for setup instructions.\nThis relies on your docker container name being \"valheim\". To do so in docker-compose, set the services `container_name` property.",
